metadata.description: Photo from series one of the most uncertain subject as Secret Societies. No matter what is historically true, I insist we will never know for sure, but as human beings used to have secrets, it’s always interesting to discover it. What are they hiding, for what purpose, maybe they are guarding something…What will you do, If you'll have to keep some knowledge in secret because of its mightiness…
